## 📁 Project Structure

```
qa_tests/
├── conftest.py                    # Fixtures: WebDriver setup/teardown, screenshot on fail
├── pytest.ini                     # Pytest config: markers, reporting, logging
├── requirements.txt               # selenium, webdriver-manager, pytest, pytest-html
├── run_tests.py                   # CLI runner (--headless, --suite flags)
│
├── pages/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   └── login_page.py              # Page Object Model (POM) — all locators/actions
│
├── utils/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   └── helpers.py                 # Credentials, ExpectedMessages, utility functions
│
├── tests/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── test_ui_elements.py        # Suite 1: UI element validation (11 tests)
│   ├── test_positive_login.py     # Suite 2: Positive/happy-path login (6 tests)
│   └── test_negative_login.py     # Suite 3: Negative/security/boundary (13 tests)
│
├── screenshots/                   # Auto-captured screenshots per test
└── reports/
    └── final_report.html          # Full pytest-html report
```

