## 🔍 Key Discoveries During Exploration

| Finding | Detail |
|---|---|
| Login is **modal-based** | Clicking "Sign In" nav button opens an overlay — not a separate page |
| Inputs have **no id/name** | Located by `type='email'` and `type='password'` |
| Email placeholder | `you@example.com` |
| Password placeholder | `••••••••` |
| Auth backend | **Supabase** — two distinct error messages |
| Valid creds signal | `"Email not confirmed"` (password correct, email unverified) |
| Invalid creds signal | `"Invalid login credentials"` |
| No rate-limiting | 5 rapid failures — no lockout triggered |

