## ✅ Suite 2 — Positive Login Tests (6/6 Passed)

> **Context:** QAPilot uses Supabase Auth with email confirmation.
> Correct password → `"Email not confirmed"` | Wrong password → `"Invalid login credentials"`

| Test ID | Description | Result | Finding |
|---|---|---|---|
| TC_POS_001 | Valid credentials → distinct server response | ✅ PASS | `"Email not confirmed"` ≠ `"Invalid"` |
| TC_POS_002 | Server distinguishes valid vs wrong password | ✅ PASS | Two different responses confirmed |
| TC_POS_003 | Email case-insensitive (`ADMIN@QAPILOT.COM`) | ✅ PASS | App normalises to lowercase ✅ |
| TC_POS_004 | Whitespace trimmed around email | ✅ PASS | `"  admin@qapilot.com  "` recognised ✅ |
| TC_POS_005 | Fields clearable between entries | ✅ PASS | No sticky-state issues |
| TC_POS_006 | Invalid creds produce standard error baseline | ✅ PASS | `"Invalid login credentials"` confirmed |

