| TC_NEG_006 | Non-existent email + valid password | ✅ PASS | `"Invalid login credentials"` |
| TC_NEG_007 | Error message quality (no stack traces) | ✅ PASS | Clean message, no leakage |
| TC_NEG_008 | **SQL injection** payload | ✅ PASS | Safely rejected, no server crash |
| TC_NEG_009 | **XSS** `<script>alert()` in email | ✅ PASS | No JS execution detected |
| TC_NEG_010 | 300-char input (boundary / DoS) | ✅ PASS | Handled gracefully |
| TC_NEG_011 | Whitespace-only credentials | ✅ PASS | Rejected — browser validation |
| TC_NEG_012 | Special characters (`!@#$%^&*()`) | ✅ PASS | Handled gracefully |
| TC_NEG_013 | **Brute-force**: 5 rapid attempts | ✅ PASS | All rejected, no lockout ⚠️ |

